# Vibeflip

A truly random coin flip using GPT.

## Usage

Install the package:

```sh
pip install vibeflip
```

Set your OpenAI API key as an environment variable.

```sh
export OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key
```

```python
from vibeflip import vibeflip

result = vibeflip()
print(result)
```

